# Task #135: the head is a newest-first LIST — an entry whose game is gone from the card
# (deleted, different card, no resolvable variant) falls through to the NEXT entry rather
# than the empty state, every decision logged.
desc Continue dispatcher: entry 1 gone from card -> falls through to entry 2 and resumes it
invoke ctpak
config paired
sdfile Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba
sdtext .userdata/shared/Lodor/continue-head.txt	/Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Ghost.gba\tGhost\n/Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba\tZelda\n
engine 0|RESULT downloaded=1
engine 0|
engine 0|RESULT pushed=1 staged=0
engine 0|RESULT reconciled=1
expect_exit 0
expect_trace PRES timeout=-1 msg='Continuing Zelda...'
expect_trace ENGINE --download
expect_trace EMULAUNCH rom=
expect_trace ✘ Zelda.gba'
expect_log continue: entry 1 not on card
expect_log continue: entry 2 resolved via=exact
